        "body": "Oh wait. I forgot that #6069 uses jsonschema so I think we can just add helper for:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport yaml\r\nfrom jsonschema import validate\r\nfrom dask.config import config\r\n\r\nwith open(\"/home/julia/dask/dask/dask-schema.yaml\") as f:\r\n    d = yaml.safe_load(f)\r\n    \r\nvalidate(instance=config, schema=d)\r\n```\r\n\r\nTo see what the failure looks like you can do:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nconfig[\"temporary-directory\"] = 2\r\nvalidate(instance=config, schema=d)\r\n```",
